    "title": "CLI / Terminal Mockup",
    "category": "My Experiments",
    "visual_html": "<div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden font-sans max-w-full mx-auto\">\n<div class=\"bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200 px-4 py-2 flex items-center gap-3\">\n<svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n<span class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 text-xs tracking-wide uppercase m-0\">Iterative Bug Fixing with AI</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bg-[#1e1e1e] p-4 md:p-8 flex justify-center\">\n<div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl bg-[#252526] border border-[#3c3c3c] rounded-xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col font-sans\">\n<!-- Header -->\n<div class=\"bg-[#323233] px-4 py-1.5 border-b border-[#1e1e1e] flex items-center justify-between\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n<svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-gray-400\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n<span class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-300 m-0\">Claude Chat</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"text-xs bg-[#1e1e1e] text-gray-400 px-2 py-1 rounded border border-[#3c3c3c] m-0\">Tokens: 1,024 / 200k</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Chat Window -->\n<div class=\"p-4 md:p-4 space-y-1.5\">\n<!-- System clear message -->\n<div class=\"flex justify-center\">\n<div class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 bg-[#1e1e1e] px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-[#3c3c3c] m-0\">\n                        User typed /clear - Context cleared\n                    </div>\n</div>\n<!-- User Message -->\n<div class=\"flex gap-2\">\n<div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded bg-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white shrink-0 font-bold shadow-md\">U</div>\n<div class=\"flex-1\">\n<div class=\"text-gray-400 text-xs font-semibold mb-1 m-0\">User</div>\n<div class=\"bg-[#323233] text-gray-200 p-4 rounded-lg rounded-tl-none border border-[#3c3c3c] shadow-sm text-xs\">\n<p class=\"m-0 mb-2\">Here are the bugs I found:</p>\n<ol class=\"list-decimal ml-5 space-y-1 text-gray-300 m-0\">\n<li>CM/Inches/PX buttons are not clickable.</li>\n<li>Ruler should align exactly to the edges of the screen with no padding.</li>\n<li>Add a manual device selector modal with popular devices.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Claude Message -->\n<div class=\"flex gap-2\">\n<div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded bg-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white shrink-0 shadow-md\">\n<svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M14 10h4.764a2 2 0 011.789 2.894l-3.5 7A2 2 0 0115.263 21h-4.017c-.163 0-.326-.02-.485-.06L7 20m7-10V5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-.095c-.5 0-.905.405-.905.905 0 .714-.211 1.412-.608 2.006L7 11v9m7-10h-2M7 20H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2h2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex-1\">\n<div class=\"text-purple-400 text-xs font-semibold mb-1 m-0 flex items-center gap-2\">\n                            Claude Code \n                            <span class=\"bg-green-900/50 text-green-400 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] uppercase border border-green-800 m-0\">Done</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"text-gray-300 text-xs space-y-1.5\">\n<p class=\"m-0\">Working on it... I've applied fixes to the codebase.</p>\n<div class=\"bg-[#1e1e1e] border border-[#3c3c3c] rounded-lg p-3 space-y-2 font-mono text-xs\">\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-green-400\">\n<svg class=\"w-4 h-4 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n<span class=\"m-0\">Fixed unit buttons z-index and pointer-events.</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-green-400\">\n<svg class=\"w-4 h-4 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n<span class=\"m-0\">Removed container padding so rulers are flush with screen edges.</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-green-400\">\n<svg class=\"w-4 h-4 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n<span class=\"m-0\">Created DeviceSelector.astro component with presets.</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"text-gray-400 text-xs italic m-0 mt-2\">Test these changes using `npm run dev` and let me know if you need any adjustments.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Chat Input -->\n<div class=\"p-4 border-t border-[#3c3c3c] bg-[#1e1e1e]\">\n<div class=\"bg-[#323233] border border-[#454545] rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center justify-between shadow-inner\">\n<span class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs m-0\">Type a message or /command...</span>\n<div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded bg-purple-600/50 flex items-center justify-center opacity-50\">\n<svg class=\"w-3 h-3 text-white\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7H3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "metadata_html": "<div class=\"mb-4\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">Why I saved this:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>High contrast monospaced typography</li><li>Realistic macOS traffic lights</li><li>Clean shadow elevation</li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-6\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">What I can learn:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>How to build realistic code snippets</li><li>Simulating CLI outputs in HTML</li></ul>\n</div>\n<!-- RESTORED: SOURCE METADATA -->\n<div class=\"transparent p-4 rounded border border-white/20 text-sm mt-4 hidden\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-y-2 gap-x-4\">\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Creator:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Tejas Jaware</div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Source:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-[var(--text-primary)]\"><a class=\"underline font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] hover:text-indigo-500\" href=\"paper_micro_tool.html\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation()\">AI Micro-Tools Guide</a></div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500 mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Rights:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-gray-500 text-xs italic leading-tight mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Belongs to original creator. Saved for inspiration.</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
